title: Extra Bonus Quote of the Day
text:
Extra Bonus Quote of the Day October 9, 2015 By Taegan Goddard 0 Comments 
“We just started to advertise — actually the Right to Rise PAC started to advertise, not our campaign.” 
— Jeb Bush, quoted by Iowa Public Radio , briefly confused the advertising efforts of his campaign and the super PAC that supports him. Related Posts Never miss a Political Wire post Your email address: * Please enter all required fields Correct invalid entries
